<br>
&quot;Sleep thee well.. Find your way and wait for me.  My son... My daughter.. and My love, find your way home.&quot;<br>
<br>
::her frown dipped into a smile.::<br>
<br>
&quot;And save a place for me where you wait my lovely...&quot;<br>
<br>
